[Student "S"]
{SOUTH opens 2\C.

NORTH should just respond 2NT, even with 11 points. The idea is to make a positive response (which forces 
the partnership to game level), and show extra strength later.

This time there is no need. SOUTH should bid 4\C (Gerber), and NORTH answers 4\S for 
two Aces.

Next SOUTH should ask for Kings, and when NORTH shows one King SOUTH should bid 7NT.}

